Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华老大  我们今时今日的地位  都是靠一双手打回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Boss Wah, we fought for the reputation we have here and now with our bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是今时不同往日了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But... today is not like yesteryear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能一辈子杀人放火的  对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We can't possibly spend the rest of our days with blood-soaked hands, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Right. You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华老大  闲话少说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Brother Wah, let me speak frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前两天你的手下在西沙截了我整顿货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Two days ago, your men intercepted a whole tonne of my cargo at Sai Sha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闲话少说  废话也不要讲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you wish to speak frankly, you also shouldn't waste your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华老大  你的意思是不认数？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Brother Wah, are you saying that you don't take any responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认  为什么不认呀？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Of course not! Why wouldn't I? - Then how will you make this right by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢点算好了  老冯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll make this right by you in our own time, Old Fung.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次小心一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Be careful next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华心武  你...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Wah Sam-Mou, you--
