Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是误会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's just a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华老大  你千万别杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Brother Wah, whatever you do, don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华老大  你不要杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Brother Wah, don't kill me...!
