Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  华老大...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you, Brother Wah!
