Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华老大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Brother Wah! You--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说不杀我的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You said you wouldn't kill me....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是没有杀你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I didn't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老板  这个怎么办？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Boss, what do we do with this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你失业了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're out of a job now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天到我这里来上班吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tomorrow, you start working for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  华老板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you, Boss Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  华老板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you, Boss Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要钱？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You want some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有条件？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- What are you saying? - Nothing.
