Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm not letting it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要钉死那个大麻成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have to nail that Pothead Shing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强奸我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Rape me, will he....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说  我也是为你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Listen to me, I'm only looking out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我好  怎样为我好？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Looking out for me? Looking out for me how?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场官司你输定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're gonna lose this lawsuit for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与其打输官司得罪了一个恶人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you lose the lawsuit, you'll offend someone ruthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如收了这笔钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why not take the money, and make a ruthless friend instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打过才知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're not the judge, how do you know I'll lose for sure?
