Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要乱来喂！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey! Don't do anything rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙先生  你做你的  我做我的  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mr Lung, you do you, I do me, OK?
