Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与你无关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Help me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Help me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No! Stop...! No....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回去告诉大麻成..\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Go back and tell Pothead-- - Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用串同他们一起做戏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Stop acting, you're in on it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做戏？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm acting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抗议  辩方律师暗示原告人放荡不羁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Objection! The defence is insinuating the plaintiff is wanton and unrestrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜总会的小姐是很认真去赚钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hostesses at nightclubs are trying to make an honest living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是放荡不羁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That is not "wanton and unrestrained".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在真实的世界里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In the real world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放荡不羁是不收钱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"wanton and unrestrained" is free of charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抗议不成立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Objection overruled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了节省法庭的时间和纳税人的金钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In order to stop wasting the court's time and taxpayers' money,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我代表被告人提出不答辩申请\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}as the defendant's legal representative, I enter a plea of no-contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请法庭根据原告人的证供\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In light of the testimony provided by the plaintiff
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在控方证供有疑点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}casting doubts on the prosecution's own evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而利益归于被告的大前题之下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I ask that the court rule in favour of the defendant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣判这案件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}given the benefit of the doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我认为  在法律层面上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I reason that, within the boundaries of the law,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告没有强奸原告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the defendant did not rape the plaintiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在道德观念上  他是错的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}However, from an ethical standpoint, he was in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抗议  辩方错误引导\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Objection! The defence is misleading.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法庭是讲法律的  不是讲道德的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The court is about law, not ethics!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抗议成立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Objection sustained.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记录员无需记录辩方律师最后两句话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Stenographer, disregard the last two statements by the defence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人  我陈词完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your Honour, with that, I conclude my closing statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告人毛事成起立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The defendant, Mou Si-Shing, arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣判之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Before I deliver my verdict,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先要多谢控辩双方的专业表现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I must first thank the professionalism displayed by both counsels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控方律师的代表陈词很扼要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The prosecution's arguments were brief but to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辩方律师选择不予答辩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The defence's choice to enter a plea of no-contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为法庭节省时间  我更加欣赏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}saving the court valuable time, has my utmost admiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本席现在宣判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The court now finds the defendant, Mou Si-Shing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告毛事成强奸罪名不成立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}not guilty of the charge of rape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案件无需要转最高法院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This case does not need to be referred to the Supreme Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告当庭释放  退庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The defendant is free to go. Court dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  龙律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You have my thanks, Attorney Lung.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在法庭内动手打人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You hit someone inside the courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你打的人不告你  法庭也会告你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Even if the person you hit doesn't sue you, the court will!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  知道你还做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- I know. - Why'd you do it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我老板还是我助手？这样跟我说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are you my boss or my assistant, talking to me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你老板请回来给你的助手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was hired by your boss to be your assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去那里？到第二庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Where are you off to? - Over to courtroom 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有宗打老婆的案件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's a wife beater case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真凑巧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- And then? - Having lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要吃午饭  不如一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What a coincidence, I'm also having lunch. Why don't we go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑是什么意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What does laughing mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表示答应  大家都是吃午饭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It means I'll do it since we're both having lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十二点正  正门见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}12 o'clock sharp, I'll see you at the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说我是你老板请回来给你的助手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was saying how I was hired by your boss to be your assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么简单的问题不适宜在这里说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This isn't the place to ask such simple questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 去那里？去洗手间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Where are you off to? - Into the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？ 出洗手间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- And then? - Out of the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝咖啡吗？  好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Coffee? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待会见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- I haven't seen you around lately. - You just don't see me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待会见  好  拜拜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- See you soon. - Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大情人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事考虑得怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Have you given it any thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要的不是赔偿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What I want is not compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要的是你工厂停工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What I want is for your factory to stop work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直到改善好排水系统才可复工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Fix the drainage system, and then you can resume operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们一天不停工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Every day your factory doesn't stop work,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,污水就不停地流到我的渔场里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}is another day the polluted water flows down into my fishery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的鱼快死光了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My fish are almost all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的渔场值多少钱？我把它买下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How much is your fishery worth? I'll buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有钱不是随便来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Being rich doesn't mean you can do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的渔场不卖的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My fishery is not for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听你的口气不像是做生意的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}From your tone, you don't seem like someone in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做生意也要顾全公德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Even if you're in business, you still need to be ethical.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要破坏自然生态  污染环境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't destroy the natural ecosystem, don't pollute the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的话我开始不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're starting to lose me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look, Miss Ip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是生意人  只会做生意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm a businessman, and I only know how to do business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的东西我不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I haven't a clue when it comes to anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把账单开出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Make me an offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我照单赔偿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll give you the asking price.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工厂停工我办不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Stop work at the factory? I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工厂值多少钱？我把它买下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How much is your factory? I'll buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的谈话到此为止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Our conversation ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会向法庭申请禁制令  禁止你的工厂开工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm going to court to get an injunction to stop work at your factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们法庭见吧  叶小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll see you in court then, Miss Ip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老板  我帮你干掉她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Boss, I'll help you get rid of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找个没有跟我们合作过的律师  来和她玩玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get a lawyer who hasn't really worked for us to play with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事上了法庭就会审讯很长时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If this thing makes it to court, it'll be a very long game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶货期间  千万不要影响工厂生产\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're too busy with production to let anything happen to the plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Have some tea. - Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文律师  很久没见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Attorney Man, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不见你去马场？最近大多是出海\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Hey, why haven't I seen you at the track? - I've been out at sea a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我来介绍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是温美玲小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is Miss Wan Mei-Ling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是港大地理系讲师  水质学专家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A geography lecturer at HK University, expert in water quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是我们这案件的主要证人  你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- She is our chief witness in this case. - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是龙约翰律师  这案件是他办的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is Attorney Lung Yeuk-Hon. He is in charge of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- How do you do? - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Attorney Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始谈正经事了  好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Let's get down to business. - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这份资料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Some printouts.
