Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！是我呀  积奇？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已说过我是积奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I told you I was Jackie!
