Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That was me.
