Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电灯的开关也找不到？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You can't even find a light switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There.
