Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想借助你的飞檐走壁功夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just wanna borrow your rooftop-flying, wall-running kung fu, Brother Biao,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我入屋装偷听器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to break into a house... and install a bug for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这样养鱼的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Is that how you keep fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要加糖和奶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't add sugar and don't add milk.
