Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说我想你帮我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh... I said I want you to help me--
