Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鱼  是象征我的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}These fish... represent my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不断前进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Constantly moving forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:17:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永不回头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}never looking back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找我干什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What'd you want from me?
