Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先透一透气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's get some fresh air first!
