Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两种主义是不同的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Both ideologies are different.
