Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说请你帮我安装一个偷听器在屋里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm telling you to put a bug inside a house for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安装偷听器这么没道德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Something as unethical as installing a bug...
