Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No way!
