Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我弄错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真大意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why are you so clumsy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  人生路不熟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please excuse me. I'm new here and still don't know my way around.
