Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么多行李  我帮你拿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You've got so much luggage, I'll give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  麻烦你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My sincerest apologies. Sorry for all the trouble.
