Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  认识了就好  一次生两次熟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Whatever, at least we've met now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三次盖着棉胎一起熏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Third time it's under the duvet doing bends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的见面只是例行会面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yesterday's meeting was just exchanging pleasantries.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看有没有可能庭外和解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's see if we can settle this out of court.
