Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是自卑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm not self-loathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是太笨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm just an idiot.
