Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有理想不要紧  有没有责任心也不要紧喂！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It doesn't matter if he has ideals. It doesn't matter if he's responsible.
