Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那岂不是任何男人都可以？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Geez... Then that means any man will do!
