Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不怕困难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Fear no obstacles!
