Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.79,0:24:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别叫了 快打999\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Stop screaming! Hurry and call the police!
