Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.49,0:43:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文武双全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He's got brains and brawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.79,0:43:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不算有来头？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That still makes him a nobody?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.25,0:43:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道要在额头上刻着 426 三个字才算有来头吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Do you have to have "Ironside 426" carved into your forehead to be somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.50,0:43:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那条船好漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That boat over there's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.09,0:43:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带你去那条船更漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The one I'm taking you to is even prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.73,0:43:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hello? They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.61,0:43:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.11,0:43:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.71,0:43:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mr Lung.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.97,0:43:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Miss Wan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.84,0:44:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？喜不喜欢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So? Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.68,0:44:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但夸张了一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But it's a bit over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.26,0:44:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不夸张  值得的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's not over the top, it's worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.02,0:44:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃午餐本来是件单调的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Lunch is inherently such a one-note thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.89,0:44:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果稍为点缀一下就不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If there's any way to spice it up, it makes all the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.19,0:44:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,积奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Wow, Jackie?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.03,0:44:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是每一顿都是这样吃吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You don't eat like this every day, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.99,0:44:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要看是不是每顿都是跟你吃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, depends if I eat with you every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.46,0:44:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢有这么多人服侍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't like so many people attending to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.42,0:44:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一个人服侍你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh! Next time it'll just be me serving you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.38,0:44:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这顿饭不便宜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A meal like this isn't cheap....
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.04,0:44:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这顿我是用老婆本请你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I dipped into my nest egg to treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.84,0:44:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你那天在我家没吃饱的补偿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Take it as repayment for leaving you with an empty stomach at my place that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.09,0:44:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱用老婆本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You shouldn't misuse a nest egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.59,0:44:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃顿午饭  不一定找到老婆的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You won't necessarily start a nest after one lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.34,0:44:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用老婆本的利息好了  干杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, I'll still have the interest. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.44,0:45:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我想去洗手间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please excuse me, I want to use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.49,0:45:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  带温小姐去洗手间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}OK. Take Miss Wan to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.41,0:45:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.79,0:45:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温小姐  这条船是龙先生包了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Miss Wan, this entire boat has been booked out by Mr Lung.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.79,0:45:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有兴趣试用男厕？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Can I interest you in trying out the gents?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.83,0:45:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有  请\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- No. - Oh, after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.63,0:45:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温小姐  请\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Miss Wan, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.81,0:45:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！在上面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey! He's up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.85,0:45:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hurry up! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.38,0:45:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.01,0:46:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I see him! He's inside here!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.11,0:46:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分头追\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Split up and chase!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.81,0:48:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.69,0:48:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这顿饭我们又要到此为止了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Our meal has come to an end again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.61,0:48:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.28,0:48:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.51,0:48:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些花快被淹死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're drowning your flowers to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.89,0:49:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶小姐  过来一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Miss Ip... Come over here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.31,0:49:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？捉贼英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What is it, heroic thief catcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.69,0:49:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了英雄怎么没有奖励？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's not much of a reward for becoming a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.90,0:49:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送一盆花给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How about some flowers, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.65,0:49:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你自己送给我一晚更实际\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Giving me a night alone with you is more practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.20,0:49:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一晚的时间  我们可以吃很多东西  讲很多话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In a single night, we can have a lot to eat, and a lot of conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.45,0:49:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家已经是好邻居了  不妨做个好朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're already such good neighbours. Why not also be good friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.08,0:49:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友是用来出卖的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Friends are for betraying.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.21,0:49:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友少  可以少做一点出卖人的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Fewer friends means less betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.21,0:49:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意被你出卖  你的眼睛已经出卖你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- I'm willing to be betrayed by you. - Your eyes have already betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.84,0:49:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼告诉我  你不是有诚意交朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your eyes tell me that you're not sincere about making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.76,0:49:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有兴趣找个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're only interested in finding a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.93,0:49:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是有兴趣找个女人做朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I am interested in finding a woman to be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.31,0:49:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信我的嘴  不要相信我的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Trust in my lips, don't trust in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.64,0:49:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的嘴有个疤  我怎么相信你？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your mouth has a scar, how can I possibly trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.61,0:49:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个疤是属于鼻子的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This scar... counts as being part of my nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.11,0:49:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要弄错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't get it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.11,0:49:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管错或对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Whether I'm wrong or right,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.40,0:49:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的邀请  心领了  拜拜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I appreciate your invitation, but I decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.11,0:49:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要心领\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't appreciate and decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.45,0:49:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭嘛  你每天也要吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's only dinner. You have to eat every day anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.54,0:50:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let go....
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.08,0:50:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们男人除了约女人看电影、吃饭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You men... apart from asking women out for dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.04,0:50:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就没有其他事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}there's nothing else to you....
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.13,0:50:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There is more!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.34,0:50:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那是最高的理想  我只放在心里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But those are the highest ideals. I only keep those in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.09,0:50:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我在玻璃屋餐厅等你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now then, I'll be waiting for you at the Glasshouse Restaurant tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.09,0:50:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I won't come...!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.88,0:50:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直等你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll keep waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.43,0:50:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不见不散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I won't leave until I see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.14,0:50:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I won't be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.02,0:50:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You have to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.18,0:50:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天长地久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}As wide as the heavens, as endless as the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.48,0:50:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海枯石烂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Until the oceans run dry and the rocks break apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.81,0:50:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直等到你来  我一定不会去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- I will wait until you come! - I definitely won't be going!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.39,0:51:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He really came...!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.73,0:51:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  我要打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Miss, I need to make a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.44,0:51:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  我也要打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mister, I also have to make a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.23,0:51:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你慢慢打吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh! Take your time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.28,0:51:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你能等多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's see how long you'll wait....
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.20,0:51:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小男人  说好不见不散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That wimp... What happened to "I won't leave until I see you"?
