Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.83,0:52:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你怎么想的 你想看看  我是不是真的见不到你就不走嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You really wanted to see if I wasn't going to leave until I saw you, right?
