Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.09,0:56:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钓来钓去都是钓自己的鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All this fishing, and we're just catching your own fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.51,0:56:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点兴奋感也没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's no sense of excitement at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.27,0:56:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钓鱼的乐趣不是在鱼上钓的一刹那\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The pleasure of fishing isn't found in the moment you reel in a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.15,0:56:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在吃鱼的一刹那？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Is it in the moment you eat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.11,0:56:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.07,0:56:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在钓鱼这段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's in the actual time spent fishing,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.61,0:56:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耐心等候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}when you're patiently waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.03,0:56:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心境宁静平和\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}your mind and soul at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.66,0:56:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么水上人家的皱纹特别多呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then how come those who live on the water have so many wrinkles?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.58,0:56:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再挖苦我  我不理你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you keep being a smart arse, I'll stop talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.84,0:57:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有想过把渔场卖掉？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Have you ever thought about selling the fishery?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.43,0:57:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.39,0:57:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卖掉它  跟我去澳洲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sell it, and come with me to Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.19,0:57:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那边开牧场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We'll open a ranch over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.10,0:57:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起养牛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We'll raise cattle together.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.65,0:57:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挤奶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Milk them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.15,0:57:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你放心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.65,0:57:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大部份时间我们是一起骑马\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Most of our days will be spent horse riding together,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.61,0:57:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奔驰于翠绿的草原之上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}galloping upon the emerald green grassland.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.12,0:57:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海阔天空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}As boundless as the sea and sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.58,0:57:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑马溜溜的山上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}On the mountain where the horses are a-galloping, a-galloping
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.33,0:57:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一朵溜溜的云哟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There is a-drifting, a-drifting a single cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.13,0:57:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,端端溜溜的照在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A silvery, silvery reflection
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.30,0:57:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康定溜溜的城哟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A-washing, a-washing over a city of Kangding
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.18,0:58:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮弯弯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The curved, curved moon
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.31,0:58:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康定溜溜的城哟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A-basking, a-basking over a city of Kangding
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.14,0:58:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这算是求婚？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That counts as a proposal, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.11,0:58:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么也好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm happy with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.61,0:58:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个人很无所谓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm a very easy-going person.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.78,0:58:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你一个秘密喂！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let me tell you a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.53,0:58:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.70,0:58:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸遗嘱规定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My father's will stipulates
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.29,0:58:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果谁人成为他的女婿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that whoever becomes his son-in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.58,0:58:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会自动承受整个渔场了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}will automatically inherit this entire fishery.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.63,0:58:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会这样反应？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey! What's with your reaction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.63,0:58:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把这个大的秘密告诉了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You've told me such a big secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.51,0:58:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无缘无故多了一个秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now out of the blue, I've got a new secret to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.76,0:58:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负担忽然大了很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All of a sudden my burdens have grown so much heavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.89,0:58:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.27,0:58:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is my own secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.94,0:58:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是口无遮拦的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have loose lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.60,0:58:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知可不可以替你保守这个秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't know if I can keep this secret of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.69,0:58:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以觉得负担很重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's why I feel like this is a heavy burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.69,0:58:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当作是自己的秘密就行了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just treat it as a secret of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.78,0:58:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当作是自己的秘密？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Treat it as my own secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.25,0:59:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是好多了？好得多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.75,0:59:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,处理自己的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Having to deal with a secret of your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.58,0:59:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感受是不一样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}it's such a different feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.76,0:59:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那遥远的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In a faraway place
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.84,0:59:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有位老姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There is an old maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.61,0:59:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面有人按门铃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Someone's ringing the doorbell!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.49,0:59:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要理会他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.16,0:59:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他再按下去会惊动警卫的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If he keeps ringing it, he'll alert security though!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.54,0:59:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去搞定他吧  知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Go and take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.80,0:59:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁呀？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.51,0:59:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是董德彪  来找毛医生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm Tung Tak-Biao. I'm here to see Dr Mo.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.80,1:00:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,董德彪嘛  我今天很忙  没有空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tung Tak-Biao, right? I'm real busy today so I'm not free.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.84,1:00:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有空  我有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're not free, but I am!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.18,1:00:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不看我  我烧了你的医务所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you don't see me, I'll burn down your clinic!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.85,1:00:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.85,1:00:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点搞定他  别吵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Just hurry up and take care of it! - Be quiet. Be quiet now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.98,1:00:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  有什么就在对讲机说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Alright! Talk to me through the intercom, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.90,1:00:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生  我给朋友出卖了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Doctor, I've been betrayed by my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.65,1:00:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉我  我该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You tell me what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.65,1:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情的开始就在一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It all started on a night where the sky was bright,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.03,1:00:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天朗气清之夜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and the air was clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.28,1:00:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My friend came to visit me,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.66,1:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说想借我飞檐走壁的本领\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}wanting to borrow my rooftop flying and wall-running abilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.41,1:00:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙很麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This guy's real annoying!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.83,1:00:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本着见义勇为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}With Bravery for the sake of justice,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.29,1:00:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大义凛然 义薄云天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Uphold justice to inspire awe, Righteousness ascending the clouds,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.83,1:00:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,义本无言的精神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and Justice needs not be said as my tenets,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.46,1:00:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是决定两肋插刀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I decided to put my life on the line,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.96,1:00:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慷慨赴义  为朋友走一趟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and vehemently serve justice to lend a friend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.97,1:00:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎知道事与愿违\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}However, it didn't go according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.76,1:00:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一再失手  任务未完成就给人抓住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I made a misstep, and before I could finish my mission, I was captured.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.31,1:00:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用再说下去了  杀死所有证人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You can stop there. Just take out all the witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.60,1:00:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死所有证人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Take out all the witnesses?!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.85,1:00:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对呀  杀死所有证人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's right! Take out all of the witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.81,1:00:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用坐牢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then you won't have to go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.36,1:00:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你医生  这次的诊金该怎样付\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thanks, Doctor! How can I pay you this time?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.78,1:00:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次是免费的 你走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's free this time. You can go.
