Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.14,1:03:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你神经病  我没神经病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Have you lost it?! - I haven't lost it!
