Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.74,1:04:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用多说  快点走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I've heard enough, hurry up and leave!
