Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.89,1:05:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用多说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Say no more!
