Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.21,1:05:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要挑日子吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Like you have to set a date....
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.01,1:05:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打你根本不用挑时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't need to find the time to hit you!
