Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.29,1:06:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们报了警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We've already called the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.83,1:06:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有本事你们继续打吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you have it in you, just keep on fighting, then!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.81,1:06:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到我口也干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I talked so much, I dried up all my saliva.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.73,1:06:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放电放到  发电机也干了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I flirted so much, I used up all my juice and the power generator's too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.69,1:06:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才让署长不告你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All that just to sweet talk the police chief from charging you guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.44,1:06:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三个人加起来有一百岁了 还要到处打架\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's like a hundred years between the three of you,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.19,1:06:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要打架？是不是为了女人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and you're still fighting like kids on the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.74,1:06:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让一让\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Excuse me. Coming through.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.75,1:06:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瘦的是为了两个女人  肥的是为了一个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why were you guys fighting anyway? Was it over a woman?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.34,1:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是为了两个男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And for me, it was two men.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.56,1:07:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我天未亮就起床为了你这个男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was up before the sun was out today for the sake of a man.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.73,1:07:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎样报答我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So how are you gonna repay me?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.20,1:07:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.24,1:07:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我失恋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.66,1:07:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你恋的是我  你就不会失恋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you had given your heart to me, you wouldn't be heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.09,1:07:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在死了那么多鱼  怎么办？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now that so many fish have died, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.46,1:07:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What do we do...?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.72,1:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那间厂简直是制造毒药的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That factory has to be for making drugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.10,1:07:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信你不走开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}As if you won't get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.98,1:07:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信你不刹车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}As if you won't hit the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.32,1:07:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎样？好狗不挡路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The hell you trying to pull?! A good dog doesn't block the road!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.86,1:07:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是好狗  你也不是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- I'm not a good dog. - You're not a good person either!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.11,1:08:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是好人  好人是不会欺骗别人感情的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- I am a good person! - They don't toy with other's emotions!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.74,1:08:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有欺骗你的感情  我自己也把真感情流露了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I never toyed with your emotions! I also exposed my true feelings!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.24,1:08:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲空话  你感觉不到吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Empty words! - Can't you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.41,1:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉不到  我对你完全没感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I can't feel it! I have no feelings for you whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.46,1:08:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你浪费我的时间  你浪费我的感情  你下流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You waste my time, you waste my emotions. You're a low-life!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.09,1:08:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了佣金  你出卖我  你出卖你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}To make your commission, you betrayed me... and yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.31,1:08:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不避开我？避开你我就不会来找你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Why didn't you get away? - If I wanted that, I wouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.94,1:08:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么危险的事你也做？  这种人不死也没有用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- How could you do something so dangerous? - This kind of person is better off dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.94,1:08:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说你  如果被他抢去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was talking about you! If he snatched the spanner off you,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.11,1:08:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止打死你  打死我也可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}he wouldn't have just killed you; he could've killed me too!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.40,1:08:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm not that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.86,1:08:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你听我解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.12,1:08:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当初是为了让你卖掉渔场而认识你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}At first, I really did come-on to you so I could persuade you to sell the fishery.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.99,1:08:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但相处下来  我发觉我真的喜欢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But as we spent more time together, I realised I had actually fallen for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.79,1:08:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的胃口越来越大  想做渔场老板？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your appetite is insatiable. Now you want to be the fishery boss too?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.75,1:08:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的确有想过这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's something I've actually thought about, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.79,1:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了表示我喜欢你是不含杂质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But to show my feelings for you are pure and true,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.34,1:08:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把渔场捐给慈善机构  然后才嫁给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you can donate the fishery to charity before you marry me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.80,1:09:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩岂不是要吃西北风？吃风就吃风  不是吃屎就行了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then we'll live on air if we have to. As long as we don't have to eat shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.31,1:09:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,渔场捐不捐给人家也要吃西北风了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Even if I don't donate the fishery, we'll still have to live on air alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.48,1:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面那家工厂一直把污水流下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Polluted water continues to flow down from the factory.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.94,1:09:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你进去看看他们干什么  好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll go in the factory and find out for you what the hell they're doing, OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.82,1:09:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们上车吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's get in the car, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.11,1:09:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！她叫你上车  你就上车吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey! She tells you to get in the car, and you just get in the car?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.63,1:09:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有朋友来找你呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your friend's here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.68,1:09:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿玲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ling....
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.64,1:09:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么也不用说  要说就在法庭上说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You don't have to say anything. If you have something, say it in court.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.85,1:09:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小心一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You be careful now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.57,1:09:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I really wanna help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.78,1:10:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但没办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I can't!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.49,1:10:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有恶意的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have no malicious intent.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.70,1:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来只不过  是求你们撤销控诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm only here to beg you to drop the charges against me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.95,1:10:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用求我们  我决定不告你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You don't have to beg. I've decided not to sue you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.16,1:10:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望你不要再在我面前出现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My only wish is that you never show your face around me ever again.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.70,1:10:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ah...! Such is not a troublesome request.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.66,1:10:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.58,1:10:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只针对我  而不针对你？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why do they only have it in for me but not for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.96,1:10:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是爱情的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is the power of love.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.01,1:10:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我做一点事可不可以？ - 可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Hey! Can you do something for me? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.30,1:10:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲明是没钱收的哦  我做事一向都是没钱收的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- There's no money in it, though. - I've always worked for free.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.80,1:10:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.16,1:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.28,1:10:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用这样也可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, you don't have to act like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.04,1:10:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is called being cautious.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.96,1:10:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们分头行事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Alright, we'll split up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.71,1:10:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二十分钟后在这里集合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We'll meet back here in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.55,1:11:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把你照进去  证明你在做事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I've got you in the shot as proof you actually did something.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.05,1:11:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.50,1:13:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么工厂？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What kind of a factory is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.16,1:13:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.04,1:13:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sorry for the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.54,1:13:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.13,1:13:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  再见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.01,1:13:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, how is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.60,1:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？没什么  是望远镜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- What's all this?! - Nothing, they're just binoculars.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.52,1:14:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛拿我的东西？  抓住他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Hey! Why're you taking my stuff?! - Get 'im!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.48,1:14:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要动  你们不可以动我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't move! You're not allowed to lay a hand on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.85,1:14:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肥佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Fatso?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.94,1:14:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么进来的？  好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- How'd you get in here?! - How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.34,1:14:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.55,1:14:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要让他走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't let him leave!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.51,1:14:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  逼我做拼命三郎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Alright, then. Guess I'm forced to play Daredevil Third Brother.
