Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.58,1:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家不用怕  他已经动不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Everyone calm down! He's got nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.54,1:15:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他绑起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tie him up for me!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.13,1:15:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地方法院民事诉讼案第二三四六号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}District Court, Civil Case No. 2346.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.38,1:15:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶氏渔场申请禁制令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ip Fishery's application for an injunction
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.63,1:15:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禁止华氏化工厂继续生产\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to halt the continued production at Wah Chemical Plant.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.09,1:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始聆讯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Court is now in session.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.89,1:16:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案件由审判专员罗忠淮主审\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The Honourable Judge Law Chung-Wai presiding.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.44,1:16:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  为什么绑着我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let go of me-- Why have you tied me up...?!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.63,1:16:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他醒了  再给他打针\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If he wakes up, give him another dose.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.73,1:16:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死肥佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Damn fatty...!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.23,1:16:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于本人与原诉人有亲戚关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Due to the familial relationship between the plaintiff and myself,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.90,1:17:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了以示公证  有关一切样本化验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to ensure that my own test results were not tainted by personal bias,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.90,1:17:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是交由香港大学海洋生物系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I handed the samples over to Hong Kong University
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.12,1:17:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一群研究工作人员做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}where researchers in the Department of Marine Biology conducted further tests.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.45,1:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据他们化验的结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}From their testing, they concluded
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.29,1:17:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水质含铅量比我检验的高百分之二\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the lead content in the water was 2% higher than my own results,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.00,1:17:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,含氧量低百分之三\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}while oxygen levels were 3% lower.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.23,1:17:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  温小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you very much, Miss Wan.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.06,1:17:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人  我问完了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No further questions, Your Honour.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.45,1:17:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与讼人律师  这案件是民事诉讼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Counsel for the defendant, this is a hearing for a civil case.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.46,1:17:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,证人所给的是专业上的供词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The testimony provided by the witness is expert opinion.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.29,1:17:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.54,1:17:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要用刑事案惯用的心理战术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}refrain from the psychological tactics employed in criminal cases.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.21,1:18:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  法官大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Understood, Your Honour.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.48,1:18:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温美玲小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Miss Wan Mei-Ling.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.19,1:18:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要忘记  你在作供之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please do not forget that before taking the stand,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.44,1:18:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you took an oath.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.94,1:18:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里所说的话  句句属实  并无虚言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Everything you say up here is the truth, and nothing but the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.49,1:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有忘记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.99,1:18:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温美玲小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Miss Wan Mei-Ling,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.24,1:18:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请以至诚作供  回答以下这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}please answer with utmost sincerity, the following question.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.50,1:18:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爱不爱我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.13,1:18:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可以这样问的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Is he allowed to ask that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.38,1:18:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抗议  与本案无关  抗议无效  与你无关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Objection! Irrelevant to the case! - Objection overruled! Irrelevant to you!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.63,1:18:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.76,1:18:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抗议有没有效  由我来决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Whether an objection is overruled is left for me to decide!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.43,1:18:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与讼人律师  请你解释为什么你要问这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Counsel for the defendant, please explain why you have to ask this question.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.48,1:18:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.14,1:18:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your Honour.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.48,1:19:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你相信我有足够理由问这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please understand that I have sufficient reasoning behind this question.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.61,1:19:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要她回答了这个问题  我会解释原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}As long as she answers the question, I will provide an explanation afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.86,1:19:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温小姐  你爱不爱他？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Miss Wan, do you love him?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.28,1:19:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人  是否只该谈水质的问题？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your Honour, shouldn't we revert back to the issue of water quality?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.08,1:19:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是以水质专家的身份来这里作证的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I am on the stand in my capacity as an expert on water quality.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.21,1:19:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是一位水质专家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I know you are an expert on water quality.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.54,1:19:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你是一位水质专家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}However, you are an expert in water quality,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.54,1:19:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时又是一个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and a woman all the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.21,1:19:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法庭可以拒绝一个男人去问第二个...男人爱不爱他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The court may object to one man asking another man if he loves him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.13,1:19:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是不正常的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Because that is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.76,1:19:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在是一个男人  问一个女人爱不爱他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}However, we now have a man asking a woman if she loves him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.93,1:19:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是很正常的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is not unusual at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.43,1:19:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且是合法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Moreover, it is legal.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.81,1:19:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找不到任何理由不准他这样问你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I cannot think of any reason to bar him from asking you such a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.36,1:19:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你一定要回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Therefore, you must provide an answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.44,1:19:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人  我不想在法庭讲爱情问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your Honour, I don't really want to discuss issues of the heart in court.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.87,1:19:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Not .
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.37,1:19:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法庭现在一定要讲爱情问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The court must now discuss issues of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.70,1:19:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爱不爱我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.92,1:20:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You must give an answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.25,1:20:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.84,1:20:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给假证供是犯了发假誓  和藐视法律的罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Giving false testimony is perjury, and you may be held in contempt of court.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.31,1:20:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.27,1:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他虽然语带恐吓  但都是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He may be trying to intimidate you, but he does speak the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.44,1:20:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  法官大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My apologies, Your Honour.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.73,1:20:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的语气可能重了一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I may have come on a bit strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.56,1:20:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这个问题  对我实在太重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But this question is just too important to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.73,1:20:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年青人对爱情认真是应该的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It is only right that young people treat love with such seriousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.03,1:20:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温美玲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Wan Mei-Ling...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.65,1:20:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要慎重回答这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You must be careful in how you answer this question.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.70,1:20:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爱还是不爱？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Do you love or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.95,1:20:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要逼我回答这个问题？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why are you having me answer this question?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.95,1:20:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在法庭以外  可以随便发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Outside the courtroom, taking an oath is like eating lettuce.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.96,1:20:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在法庭以内  誓言是有法律约束力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Inside the courtroom, an oath is granted power by the law.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.00,1:20:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说谎是需要负上刑事责任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you do not tell the truth, you face the consequences of breaking the law.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.25,1:20:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要很清楚地知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I must know, in no uncertain terms...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.59,1:20:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爱不爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}if you love me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.63,1:20:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个答案会影响我以后的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Because the answer you give will affect the future of my career,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.64,1:20:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和未来的日子将会如何渡过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}as well as how I will spend the rest of my days.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.56,1:20:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,易求无价宝  难得有情郎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It is easy to ask for a priceless treasure, but a beau is hard to come by.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.73,1:20:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是法官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I am a judge.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.98,1:21:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有权判谁有罪  谁无罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have the authority to declare who is guilty and who is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.94,1:21:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我无权判他有没有情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I do not have the authority to declare if his feelings are true.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.90,1:21:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这宗案件的法官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In this particular case, you are the judge.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.03,1:21:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在等你的判词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We are all awaiting your verdict.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.20,1:21:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.95,1:21:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.13,1:21:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your Honour.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.38,1:21:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于我们两个相爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}As the two of us are in love,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.05,1:21:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而她和我分别代表原诉和与讼人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and she represents the plaintiff, and I represent the defendant:
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.84,1:21:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了司法公证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to uphold judicial integrity,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.30,1:21:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和双方的利益\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and in the best interests of both parties involved,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.56,1:21:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个必须有一个退出本案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}one of us will need to withdraw from this case.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.60,1:21:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请法官大人批准我退出本案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I ask that Your Honour grant me permission to withdraw from the case.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.82,1:21:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准其所请\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Permission granted.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.07,1:21:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全案押后另行排期聆讯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All hearings for the case are postponed to a later date.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.95,1:22:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么做事的？臭男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Do you even know how to do your job? - Pigs...!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.89,1:22:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你平时不给我机会说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's your own fault for not giving me a chance to say it normally.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.68,1:22:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只好在法庭上说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So I had no other choice but to say it in court.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.14,1:22:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用找了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Here, keep the change.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.44,1:22:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.19,1:22:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小姐  我是逼不得已才被你看到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm sorry, miss. There was nothing I could do to not be seen by you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.99,1:22:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.74,1:22:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.04,1:22:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.29,1:22:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事  你先回去  我再找你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh! Nothing. You can get going, I'll see you another time.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.79,1:22:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We'll get going, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.38,1:22:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己坐车回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Catch a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.63,1:22:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有要紧事要做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I've got something important to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.89,1:22:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.61,1:23:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.74,1:23:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚就在这里开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}OK, so this is where it all started.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.41,1:23:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他由那边走  我由这边走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He went that way. I went this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.08,1:23:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里等我  不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Wait for me here. - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.00,1:23:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面可能很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It might be really dangerous inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.71,1:23:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我照顾不了你的  我会照顾自己的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- I'm not scared. - I can't take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.38,1:23:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会照顾自己的  清楚了吗？  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- I can take care of myself. - ...came back here. What should I do, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.31,1:23:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上它  干什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Put this on. - What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.89,1:23:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一会就有用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It'll be useful in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.41,1:23:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿彪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Biao.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.08,1:24:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Be careful. - You be careful too.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.04,1:24:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey! Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.04,1:24:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.41,1:24:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拖他出去  扔到大海里  知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Drag him outside. Toss him into the sea! - Understood.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.66,1:24:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.16,1:24:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.80,1:24:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't do anything stupid!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.05,1:24:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来找人的  什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- We're looking for someone. - What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.47,1:25:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来找人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.30,1:25:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有你们要找的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's no one here you're looking for!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.31,1:25:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Whaddya mean no one here?!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.56,1:25:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他一起来的  等了很久也不见他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I came here with him. I waited around and never saw him leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.10,1:25:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定还在这里  所以我们来是没有错的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He must be here! So we were right in coming here!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.31,1:25:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.56,1:25:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在法庭里是你凶  在这里是我凶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The courtroom is your turf. This here is my turf.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.73,1:25:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走  什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Get out! - What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.65,1:25:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不要乱来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's not do anything rash.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.49,1:25:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.91,1:25:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在这里制造毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're making drugs here...!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.33,1:25:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Take care of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.05,1:25:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过我不能照顾你的  我说过不用你照顾的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- I told you I couldn't take care of you! - And I told you I didn't need you to.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.16,1:26:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不相信连你也摆不平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's no way even I couldn't finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.41,1:26:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王飞雄...你怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Wong Fei-Hung! Wong Fei-Hung, how you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.67,1:26:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的头很晕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm really high....
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.94,1:29:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人渣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Human scum!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.63,1:29:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我摆平他  这工厂给你一半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Take care of him for me, and half of this plant is yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.76,1:29:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.85,1:31:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王八蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.14,1:32:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王飞雄  你怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Wong Fei-Hung, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.85,1:32:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报警呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Turn the dial...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.56,1:32:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报警呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}C-Call the police...!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.33,1:33:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死八婆  告我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Fucking bitch... Sue me?!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.33,1:33:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄得我的工厂这么乱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You've made a real mess of my plant!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.35,1:33:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的手很痛呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My hand really hurts...!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.89,1:33:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不痛我就不用踩你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I wouldn't be stepping on you if it didn't hurt!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.53,1:33:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我打毒针\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You injected me with a drug needle?!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.57,1:34:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}See you later, mate.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.74,1:35:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿玲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ling!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.75,1:35:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？还痛不痛？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How are you feeling?
